      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:6:8:30:10",
      "text": [
        " رَأَيْتُ أَبَا جَعْفَرٍ ( عليه السلام ) يَخْتَضِبُ بِالْحِنَّاءِ خِضَاباً قَانِياً ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Muhammad Bin Yahya, from Ahmad Bin Muhammad, from Muhammad Bin Khalid, from Fazalat Bin Ayoub, from Muawiya Bin Ammar who said, ",
          "‘I saw Abu Ja’far<sup>asws</sup> dyeing with the henna, a red dyeing’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "10. Muhammad ibn Yahya has narrated from Ahmad ibn Muhammad, from ibn Khalid from Fadalah ibn Ayyub from Mu‘awiyah ibn ‘Ammar who has said the following: “I saw abu Ja’far, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, had applied hair dye with henna of red color.’” "
        ]
      }
